00:35:19,050 --> 00:35:21,600
而且"支那"是中国
And by the way, Henry "Chink Land" implies China.

336
00:35:21,650 --> 00:35:24,400
我是在泰国 是不同的国家
I was in Thailand, it's a different country.

337
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:26,990
我的手机
Hey, my phone!

338
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:31,040
别动
Hold it right there.

339
00:35:34,390 --> 00:35:36,410
大家趴下来
Everybody down on the ground!

340
00:35:36,450 --> 00:35:38,550
别开枪
Quit shooting!

341
00:35:39,300 --> 00:35:40,720
你找错人了
You got the wrong guy.

342
00:35:40,740 --> 00:35:43,160
等警长来再说
We'll let the sheriff sort it out when they get here.

343
00:35:43,230 --> 00:35:46,480
- 你没事吧？- 我搞定他们了
- Are you okay? - I got it under control!

344
00:35:46,530 --> 00:35:47,820
我没有杀人
I didn't kill anybody.

345
00:35:48,240 --> 00:35:50,290
妈的
Shit!

346
00:35:53,410 --> 00:35:56,400
你是厄尔吗？
You Earl?

347
00:35:57,080 --> 00:35:59,790
你做的早餐超好吃
Loved your French toast.

348
00:36:01,670 --> 00:36:03,710
- 趴下来 - 我就说…
- Down. - Like I said...

349
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:06,970
- 我喜欢悍一点的妞儿 - 谢了
- I love a girl who can take care of herseIf. - Thanks.

350
00:36:07,030 --> 00:36:10,640
你上了新闻 跟你打架的小黑 他挂了
You're on the news. That guy you got in a fight with is dead.

351
00:36:10,670 --> 00:36:14,480
- 亨利要拿回他的毒品 - 你怎么不还给他？
- Henry set me up. He wants his drugs back. - Why don't you give them back.

352
00:36:14,520 --> 00:36:18,050
- 不行 那是我唯一的保障 - 昨晚我们一起
- I can't. It's the only insurance I got. - You were with me last night.

353
00:36:18,050 --> 00:36:20,030
- 你有不在场证明 - 趴下来 厄尔
I'm your alibi. Down, Earl!

354
00:36:20,080 --> 00:36:22,140
去跟警察说呀
Tell the cops.

355
00:36:22,160 --> 00:36:25,020
警察不是唯一的麻烦
Right now it ain't the cops that I'm worried about.

356
00:36:25,050 --> 00:36:26,610
情况不妙
Not good.

357
00:36:26,620 --> 00:36:28,820
- 死神帮来了 - 他说的对 夏恩
- Reapers! - He's right, Shane.

358
00:36:28,870 --> 00:36:32,110
待会再说行吗？
You think we could finish this conversation later?

359
00:36:32,910 --> 00:36:37,550
好吧 脱了险你就要报警 好吗？
All right. Once we're in the clear, you call the cops. Agreed?

360
00:36:37,780 --> 00:36:39,650
我拿这个干嘛？
What should I do with this?

361
00:36:39,730 --> 00:36:42,800
就当我没说过我喜欢悍妞
Forget what I said about liking women who can take care of themselves.

362
00:36:44,750 --> 00:36:48,980
抱歉 事情不太妙 你留下来比较安全
Sorry, it's gonna get crazy. You'll be safer here than running with us.

363
00:36:49,040 --> 00:36:51,680
- 回洛杉矶再见 - 你要我干嘛？
- See you back in L.A. - What am I supposed to do?

364
00:36:51,690 --> 00:36:53,870
陪厄尔吗？
Hang out with Earl?

365
00:37:11,100 --> 00:37:13,230
他们往哪儿走？
Which way?

366
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:17,440
快给我说 老头
Which way did you say, old man?

367
00:37:19,540 --> 00:37:23,080
- 哪个方向？- 抄小路
- Which way? - Shortcut!

368
00:37:26,240 --> 00:37:30,970
逮到他们就宰了他们
Let's catch them, kill them and bury them!

369
00:37:33,690 --> 00:37:36,660
他们追上来了 该死 越来越多人
They're still on us! Shit! There's more of them!

370
00:37:36,680 --> 00:37:39,210
- 怎么办？- 要往哪儿？
- What are we gonna do, Ford? - Where we going?

371
00:37:40,030 --> 00:37:42,930
我正在想
I'm working on it!

372
00:38:06,100 --> 00:38:08,630
他们走哪边？
Which way did they go?

373
00:38:18,930 --> 00:38:22,480
可恶 走吧
Damn! Come on!

374
00:38:46,140 --> 00:38:47,630
可以报警了吗？
Now can we call the cops?

375
00:38:47,680 --> 00:38:49,570
- 不行 - 为什么？
- No. - Why not?

376
00:38:49,570 --> 00:38:52,690
不只是警察 是麦费森
Because it's not just the cops, it's McPherson.

377
00:38:52,710 --> 00:38:53,940
麦费森？
McPherson?

378
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:56,270
抄你店的家伙
The guy that tore up your shop.

379
00:38:56,310 --> 00:38:58,320
他认为我是毒贩
He already thinks I'm a drug dealer.

380
00:38:58,350 --> 00:39:02,500
现在又认为我杀死朱利尔 所以我一定要证明…
Now he thinks I shot Junior. And he has no reason to think otherwise...

381
00:39:02,530 --> 00:39:05,760
- 自己无罪 - 真倒霉 链条断了
- unless I can prove it. - Bad just turned to worse. Bent link.

382
00:39:05,800 --> 00:39:08,850
真是屋漏偏逢连夜雨
This just keeps getting better and better.

383
00:39:08,920 --> 00:39:12,220
我的工具箱有备用链条
I got a spare in my toolkit.

384
00:39:12,490 --> 00:39:15,280
他是被勒死的
He was strangled, by the way.

385
00:39:15,330 --> 00:39:18,860
- 谁？- 朱利尔 是被机车链条勒死
- Who? - Junior. He was strangled with a bike chain.

386
00:39:19,000 --> 00:39:21,560
妈的
Shit.

387
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:25,930
是亨利用自己的机车链条
Henry used the chain off his own bike.

388
00:39:28,960 --> 00:39:30,930
- 你怎么知道？- 是啊 你怎么知道？
- How do you know that? - How do you know?

389
00:39:30,930 --> 00:39:33,430
你怎么会知道的？
Yeah, how did you know that?

390
00:39:33,620 --> 00:39:36,030
这个嘛…
Well, it's....

391
00:39:36,330 --> 00:39:37,690
事情有点复杂
It's complicated.

392
00:39:39,700 --> 00:39:42,000
- 你不左转就会去俄勒冈 - 应该右转
- You turning left, or we going to Oregon? - It's right.

393
00:39:42,010 --> 00:39:43,830
右转？怎么？
It's right? What...?

394
00:39:43,840 --> 00:39:48,390
别乱指我 我知道路
Get the finger out of my face. I know where I'm going.

395
00:39:50,670 --> 00:39:53,430
亨利这下死定了
Henry just screwed himseIf.

396
00:39:53,490 --> 00:39:55,910
- 你看到这些刮痕吗？- 嗯
- See those scratches and nicks? - Yeah.

397
00:39:55,950 --> 00:39:58,380
这是齿盘刮出来的
Well, it picks them up from the sprocket.

398
00:39:58,420 --> 00:40:01,530
每一台机车的刮痕都不同
Now, no two bikes got the same chain-wear pattern...

399
00:40:01,600 --> 00:40:04,750
因为每个齿盘的磨损痕迹都不同
because no two sprockets are the same.

400
00:40:04,830 --> 00:40:08,820
只要能证明亨利的链条是凶器
So we match the chain used to kill Junior with Henry's bike...

401
00:40:09,700 --> 00:40:12,340
就能逮到他
and we got him.

402
00:40:12,580 --> 00:40:14,620
就跟指纹一样
Like a fingerprint.

403
00:40:14,770 --> 00:40:18,320
就连你这白痴也搞懂了耶
Try not to move your lips so much when you think.

404
00:40:18,870 --> 00:40:22,010
现在可以报警了吧？
Now we call the cops, right?

405
00:40:22,560 --> 00:40:25,180
可以了
Now we call the cops.

406
00:40:27,670 --> 00:40:31,520
- 好恶心哦 - 去开房间吧
- Real cute, guys. - Get a room.

407
00:40:40,500 --> 00:40:43,700
- 麦费森？- 福特 你越来越厉害了
- McPherson, it's F... - Ford. Looks like you're trading up.

408
00:40:43,720 --> 00:40:46,480
从毒贩变成一级谋杀犯
Going from drug trafficking to first-degree murder.

409
00:40:46,490 --> 00:40:48,800
- 我被人陷害 - 这句话我常听
- I was set up. - In my business I hear that a lot.

410
00:40:48,820 --> 00:40:51,840
- 大声点 我正在侧录 - 谁会想陷害你？
- Loud. Recorder's on. - Who wants to set you up?

411
00:40:51,880 --> 00:40:54,100
亨利
Henry James.

412
00:40:54,160 --> 00:40:57,520
地狱帮老大 为什么呢？
Leader of the Hellions. Now, why would he wanna do that?

413
00:40:57,530 --> 00:41:00,320
你要找的毒品是他的
Those drugs you were looking for belong to Henry.

414
00:41:00,340 --> 00:41:03,620
你去抄店前一晚 我把货藏起来 亨利要讨回去
I stashed them the night before you raided the shop. He wants them back.

415
00:41:04,110 --> 00:41:07,780
说出毒品下落 也许我会相信
Tell me where the drugs are, I might buy that'd give Henry motive.

416
00:41:07,790 --> 00:41:12,480
- 也许我能让你脱罪 - 也许还不够好 把亨利抓起来
- Maybe we can work something out. - "Maybe" don't cut it. Arrest Henry...

417
00:41:12,560 --> 00:41:16,240
- 我就交出毒品 - 逮捕他？凭什么？
- then I'll take you to the drugs. - Arrest him? On what grounds?

418
00:41:16,280 --> 00:41:18,010
一级谋杀罪
First-degree murder.

419
00:41:18,030 --> 00:41:20,690
- 我能证明凶器出于亨利之手 - 不太可能
- What if I tie the murder weapon to Henry? - Big "if"

420
00:41:20,720 --> 00:41:22,800
逮捕他
Arrest him.

421
00:41:22,860 --> 00:41:25,360
- 去拿他的车 我就把毒品交给你 - 去拿他的车 好
- Get his bike, I'll show you. - Get his bike. Okay.

422
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:29,410
你还要我逮捕谁呢？前女友 小学老师？
Anyone else you'd like me to arrest? Ex-girlfriend, second-grade teacher...?

423
00:41:29,440 --> 00:41:32,960
- 等一下 我抄下来 - 你有没有在听
- Hold on, I'm making a list. - You're not listening to me.

424
00:41:33,030 --> 00:41:35,280
- 亨利杀死朱利尔 - 我才不信
- Henry killed Junior. - I don't know that.

425
00:41:35,300 --> 00:41:38,060
那你就帮不了我
Then you can't help me!

426
00:41:48,350 --> 00:41:50,070
这方法不管用
Well, that didn't fly.

427
00:41:50,100 --> 00:41:53,600
管它的 咱们去墨西哥吧
Screw it. Let's haul ass down to Mexico and don't look back.

428
00:41:53,760 --> 00:41:57,270
这次我也同意
As much as I hate to say it, I agree with him.

429
00:41:57,370 --> 00:42:00,620
- 我们要回洛杉矶 - 你这是自投罗网
- We're going to L.A. - Oh, yeah. That makes sense.

430
00:42:00,650 --> 00:42:03,760
我要靠亨利的毒品替我脱罪
I have to get Henry's bike. That will clear me.

431
00:42:03,790 --> 00:42:07,390
每条路都会有警方临检站
They'll have checkpoints on every dirt road between here and the coast.

432
00:42:07,440 --> 00:42:10,610
骑重型机车太招摇了
We're not exactly hard to spot driving these.

433
00:42:10,650 --> 00:42:14,680
- 你想把机车丢掉？- 不 骑车比较快
- You wanna ditch the bikes? - No, I'd rather be fast than invisible.

434
00:42:16,050 --> 00:42:19,970
如果太容易就不好玩 对吧？
Come on. Wouldn't be any fun if it was easy, right?

435
00:42:21,160 --> 00:42:24,420
我从不担心下一公里会怎样
I live my life a quarter mile at a time.

436
00:42:24,510 --> 00:42:27,730
这是我听过最蠢的话
That is the dumbest thing I've ever heard.

437
00:42:42,960 --> 00:42:45,360
每条公路都有警方临检站
Po-po got the highways blocked from here to L.A.

438
00:42:45,390 --> 00:42:46,880
洛杉矶？
L.A.?

439
00:42:47,210 --> 00:42:50,470
他怎么会笨到自投罗网？
Why would he go to the one place he know I got on lockdown?

440
00:42:50,480 --> 00:42:53,850
- 咱们在州际公路堵他 - 他没那么笨
- Let's catch him on the interstate. - No, he's smarter than that.

441
00:42:53,880 --> 00:42:56,130
他想偷溜回去
He trying to backdoor us.

442
00:42:56,170 --> 00:42:58,440
一定会穿过沙漠
He going through the Palms.

443
00:42:58,500 --> 00:43:01,700
我就会走那儿 去堵他吧
That's the way I'd go. And that's the way we going.

444
00:43:08,300 --> 00:43:13,680
亨利去年因为持有毒品入狱
You know, Henry James did pull six months in L.A. County last year for possession.

445
00:43:14,430 --> 00:43:17,050
也许福特说的有道理
Maybe Ford is onto something.

446
00:43:20,110 --> 00:43:23,470
那你就帮不了我
Then you can't help me!

447
00:43:23,880 --> 00:43:26,410
叫警方检查前往洛城的每条路
Call in. Check everything from Lone Pine and L.A.

448
00:43:26,410 --> 00:43:30,050
- 福特真的会回洛杉矶？- 他要回去找亨利
- You think Ford's going back to L.A.? - He's going after Henry James.

449
00:43:30,080 --> 00:43:33,940
如果是我被人陷害 我就会回去 走吧
If he's right and Henry did set him up, that's what I'd do. Let's go!

450
00:43:34,000 --> 00:43:37,630
- 你没付油钱 - 对喔
- You have to pay for the gas. - Oh, right.

451
00:43:54,920 --> 00:43:57,020
死神帮
Reapers!

452
00:44:06,220 --> 00:44:08,700
- 我们在沙漠甩掉他们 - 你疯了吗？
- We'll lose them in the Palms! - Are you crazy?

453
00:44:08,720 --> 00:44:10,260
我最讨厌他这样
I hate it when he does this!

454
00:44:10,270 --> 00:44:13,720
- 他们骑进树林 - 我看到了 紧跟着福特
- They going into the trees! - I could see that, fool! Stay on Ford.

455
00:44:41,470 --> 00:44:44,170
- 我快逮到他了 - 他们开枪了 福特
- I got his ass! - They're shooting at us, Ford!

456
00:44:44,370 --> 00:44:45,820
- 我知道 - 怎么办？
- I know! - What do we do?

457
00:44:45,840 --> 00:44:47,940
你往右 他们只会追我
Go right! They'll follow me!

458
00:45:20,480 --> 00:45:22,300
吃子弹吧
Meet the twins!

459
00:45:39,060 --> 00:45:41,020
来吧 福特
All right, Ford!

460
00:45:42,130 --> 00:45:44,190
咱们俩对决吧
Just you and me, baby!

461
00:46:10,720 --> 00:46:12,560
你不该欺负女生
Shouldn't pick on girls.

462
00:49:13,830 --> 00:49:15,620
你没事吧？
You all right?

463
00:49:19,920 --> 00:49:22,930
我骑车从急驶列车的车顶跳下来
I just jumped my bike onto the roof of a moving train.

464
00:49:23,200 --> 00:49:26,650
人在危急时能激发神奇的潜能
It's amazing what you can do when you have no choice.

465
00:49:31,520 --> 00:49:33,960
小威跟小刀呢？
Where are Val and DaIton?

466
00:49:34,990 --> 00:49:38,470
他赢了我 我差点就没命
He had me, dog. He had me. I was gone!

467
00:49:38,590 --> 00:49:41,110
他却及时救我一命
He's the one snatched me up out of there!

468
00:49:41,500 --> 00:49:44,770
我搞不懂 他不像是凶手
I'm trying to figure out why. He ain't acting like no killer!

469
00:49:44,820 --> 00:49:47,500
我只知道你小弟挂了 他在逃亡
Your brother's dead and cracker's on the run.

470
00:49:47,600 --> 00:49:51,830
我觉得不太对劲 这整件事感觉怪怪的
Shit don't feel right. Don't sound right, don't look right.

471
00:49:51,920 --> 00:49:54,690
只有抓到他才能搞清楚
Only way we can find out is to get our hands on him.

472
00:49:54,720 --> 00:49:58,310
- 我同意 - 那就快出发吧
- I'm with that. - Then get your black ass up and let's go!

473
00:49:58,320 --> 00:50:00,110
大伙儿走吧
Everybody, let's go!

474
00:50:11,170 --> 00:50:13,510
小威第一次骑得比你快
First time Val's beat you anywhere!

475
00:50:13,600 --> 00:50:15,920
你一定是被女人耽误了
Must be the chick.

476
00:50:16,140 --> 00:50:18,900
是啊 我停下来修个指甲
Yeah, I stopped for a manicure.

477
00:50:20,090 --> 00:50:24,560
你要听坏消息吗？每一条公路都有临检站
Want this hour's bad news? Every major road in L.A. is blocked.

478
00:50:24,820 --> 00:50:27,670
你说太容易就不好玩
I know you said it wouldn't be any fun if it was easy...

479
00:50:27,830 --> 00:50:30,680
可是也不需要这样玩命吧
but does it have to be this much fun?

480
00:50:37,590 --> 00:50:40,260
你要怎么替我脱罪？
You said you could make this go away. How?

481
00:50:40,330 --> 00:50:44,630
有时候证人很健忘
Sometimes witnesses forget what they saw.

482
00:50:44,790 --> 00:50:46,730
或是拒绝作证
Refuse to testify.

483
00:50:46,850 --> 00:50:48,430
等我回洛杉矶…
You still want your shit back...

484
00:50:48,450 --> 00:50:53,010
再把货还给你 明天下午三点
I'll call you when I get to L.A. 3:00 tomorrow afternoon.

485
00:50:55,260 --> 00:50:56,920
干嘛？
What?

486
00:51:01,390 --> 00:51:05,220
事情有点不对劲 福特不像杀人凶手
Jay, something doesn't sit with me. Ford doesn't profile up as a killer.

487
00:51:05,260 --> 00:51:08,180
你的直觉真灵光 韩德森
Yeah? Good instincts, Henderson.

488
00:51:08,390 --> 00:51:12,720
半年前我给福特一次机会 他却落跑了
Listen, I gave Ford a chance to tell the truth six months ago. He ran.

489
00:51:12,810 --> 00:51:15,830
昨晚我再次给他机会 他又落跑
I gave him another chance last night. He ran again.

490
00:51:15,870 --> 00:51:20,680
无辜的人是不会落跑的
Innocent men, Henderson, don't run.

491
00:51:22,720 --> 00:51:24,160
他上钩了
He went for it!

492
00:51:24,200 --> 00:51:28,470
现在只要躲过几百个警察就行
Now we just gotta get past the several hundred cops between us and L.A.

493
00:51:28,490 --> 00:51:31,410
希望你这次是计划好了
God, I hope you have a plan this time.

494
00:51:33,870 --> 00:51:35,370
我是有计划
Yeah, I got a plan.

495
00:51:58,690 --> 00:52:01,200
你们想撇下我吗？
You gonna leave without me?

496
00:52:09,840 --> 00:52:11,980
我的老天
Oh, my God.

497
00:52:12,200 --> 00:52:14,390
你们看
Check it out, man.

498
00:52:15,320 --> 00:52:18,100
哇塞
Holy shit.

499
00:52:22,970 --> 00:52:27,900
看到三个飚车族跟一个小妞吗？
Seen three bikers and a chick on a couple of crotch rockets in the last hour?

