509
00:52:58,960 --> 00:53:00,890
监看摄影机有用吗？
Does this thing work?

510
00:53:08,950 --> 00:53:12,040
福特 你有病吗？
Ford. What is wrong with you?

511
00:53:12,090 --> 00:53:13,600
