513
00:53:27,190 --> 00:53:30,980
你没说你为什么选择去泰国
So you never actually told me why you chose Thailand.

514
00:53:33,320 --> 00:53:37,200
我想去个不会让我想起你的地方
Well, I just wanted to go someplace that wouldn't remind me of you.

515
00:53:38,440 --> 00:53:40,200
是吗？
Oh, yeah?

516
00:53:40,240 --> 00:53:42,620
结果有用吗？
How did that work out for you?

517
00:53:44,750 --> 00:53:47,340
- 没什么用 - 是吗？
