518
00:53:48,930 --> 00:53:50,840
承认吧
Oh, come on, admit it.

519
00:53:51,690 --> 00:53:53,890
你很高兴我回来
You're so glad I came back.

520
00:53:55,040 --> 00:53:58,400
我只是这周末闲着没事干
I just had nothing better to do this weekend.

521
00:54:02,600 --> 00:54:05,520
高速公路上干嘛忽然停车？
Why we stopping in the middle of the interstate?

522
00:54:06,330 --> 00:54:07,180
临检站
Roadblock.

523
00:54:07,220 --> 00:54:11,430
你可以走了 开车吧
Sir! You're clear. Go ahead. Move it out.

524
00:54:12,060 --> 00:54:15,020
