Could we get a picture of you guys?

546
00:56:44,130 --> 00:56:48,070
我们在旅行 我们要把照片寄给各地网友
We're on a road trip, we e-mail people on our buddy list where we're at.

547
00:56:48,200 --> 00:56:49,900
