这次不要眨眼哦
This time, no blinking.

552
00:57:08,020 --> 00:57:10,140
笑一个
Smile.

553
00:57:14,610 --> 00:57:16,780
又怎么了？
Now what?

554
00:57:26,320 --> 00:57:29,530
你要懂得如何理财
It's also about financial freedom.

555
00:57:32,490 --> 00:57:36,140
- 需要帮忙吗？- 把货柜打开
- What can I do for you? - Why don't you open up the back for me.

556
00:57:38,560 --> 00:57:41,160
这辆卡车好长
That's a long truck.

557
00:57:46,550 --> 00:57:48,810
别碰我
Don't touch me.

558
00:57:51,770 --> 00:57:53,470
- 奇怪了 - 什么？
- That's weird. - What?

559
00:57:53,490 --> 00:57:55,300
锁不见了
My lock's gone.

560
00:58:19,840 --> 00:58:21,980
你在等绿灯吗？
You waiting for a green light?

561
00:58:33,800 --> 00:58:37,640
- 让一让 - 卡车抛锚 叫拖吊车
- Let's go, make a hole! - Truck's broke. Call a tow truck.

562
00:58:39,420 --> 00:58:42,670
