569
00:59:37,660 --> 00:59:39,930
不要 我要跟你走
No way, I'm going with you!

570
00:59:48,390 --> 00:59:51,940
- 你不能跟我 - 你真可恶
- No, you're not. - Goddamn it, Ford!

571
00:59:59,070 --> 01:00:02,120
