And I'm not gonna stand for it. I wanna return the bike. You can take it back.

576
01:00:36,270 --> 01:00:40,880
我不能退是什么意思？我才骑了二百多里
What do you mean I can't bring it back? Okay, there's only 200 miles on the bike.

577
01:00:41,210 --> 01:00:44,090
