If you say one more word....

578
01:00:50,100 --> 01:00:51,570
王八蛋
Asshole!

579
01:00:51,600 --> 01:00:55,070
喂？他又挂我电话
Hello? Hung up again!

580
01:01:04,030 --> 01:01:06,600
- 臭飚车族 - 你疯了 快叫支援
- Bikers. - This is crazy! We can call backup.

581
01:01:06,630 --> 01:01:11,320
你不喜欢我开车 就去搭顺风车
If you don't like my driving, Henderson, you can get out and hitch.

582
