不是吧
No way!

583
01:01:30,720 --> 01:01:35,520
幸好有安全气囊 别说话
Thank God for airbags. Shut up.

584
01:02:14,350 --> 01:02:16,740
- 来吧 福特 - 你误会我了
- Come on, Ford. - You got this wrong!

585
01:02:32,190 --> 01:02:34,450
哎呀
Damn!

586
01:02:45,920 --> 01:02:49,060
妈的 疯白人
Damn! Crazy white boy!

587
