Look, man, I don't wanna...

588
01:02:55,680 --> 01:02:58,560
你够种跟我单挑吗？
You think you man enough to drop that hammer?

589
01:02:58,680 --> 01:03:02,000
我不想 朱利尔也不是我杀的
Don't want to. I didn't kill Junior either.

590
01:03:02,030 --> 01:03:04,400
如果是的话 我就不会救你一命
If I did, I would've let you die at the tracks.

591
01:03:04,460 --> 01:03:10,220
- 你为什么不跟我解释？- 我想你一定不会听
- Why didn't you stick around and talk? - I didn't think this would go all that well.

592
01:03:11,560 --> 01:03:14,060
好吧 他是谁杀的？
All right. You didn't kill him, who did?

593
01:03:14,080 --> 01:03:17,680
是亨利 他陷害我
Henry James. He set me up.

594
01:03:20,010 --> 01:03:22,360
你要我相信你的话？
So I'm supposed to just believe what you say now?

595
01:03:22,710 --> 01:03:27,010
你等着瞧 我会逮到他
Well, see for yourseIf. I'm taking him down.

596
01:03:27,070 --> 01:03:30,550
