You don't believe me, you can always shoot me then.

597
01:03:32,880 --> 01:03:35,790
你掉了这玩意
You dropped this.

598
01:03:41,760 --> 01:03:44,440
这最好是好消息
This better be someone with good news or money.

599
01:03:44,510 --> 01:03:49,940
我可以让你逮到凶手 同时把毒品交给你
What would you say if I gave you Junior's killer and Henry's drugs at the same time?

600
01:03:50,400 --> 01:03:51,970
哪里？
Where?

601
01:03:52,000 --> 01:03:55,980
你知道地方 半年前你抄过她的店
You know the address. You busted its doors down about six months ago.

602
01:03:56,040 --> 01:03:58,940
两小时后见
Meet me there in two hours.

603
01:04:23,940 --> 01:04:26,130
安非他命
Crystal meth.

604
01:04:33,050 --> 01:04:36,240
你能不能帮帮忙？
I don't suppose we got a spare set of hands?

605
01:04:44,690 --> 01:04:46,910
- 干嘛？- 什么干嘛
- Yeah? - Don't "yeah" me.

606
01:04:46,980 --> 01:04:48,680
有什么动静？
How we doing over there?

607
01:04:48,800 --> 01:04:50,950
只有我跟一大堆鱼
It's just me and the fishes, man.

608
01:04:50,970 --> 01:04:54,230
有美人鱼我会通知你
If a mermaid pops up, I'll call you.

609
01:04:59,210 --> 01:05:01,480
- 待在道尔顿那儿 - 好
- Just stay there at Dalton's. - Yeah.

610
01:05:01,520 --> 01:05:03,530
这儿真舒适
It's lovely here.

611
01:05:03,570 --> 01:05:04,970
过一会儿见
I'll see you in a little while.

612
01:05:05,690 --> 01:05:07,700
小心点 好吗？
Just be careful, all right?

613
01:05:07,740 --> 01:05:11,440
- 你知道我的 - 所以我才会担心
- Well, you know me. - Yeah, that's why I'm worried.

614
01:05:11,640 --> 01:05:14,060
搞定了我再打给你
I'll call you when it's over.

615
01:05:21,430 --> 01:05:25,440
- 会是什么人？- 我叫了披萨
- Who the hell is that? - I ordered pizza.

616
01:05:26,340 --> 01:05:29,050
- 不会吧？- 真的
- You're kidding me, right? - No.

617
01:05:29,540 --> 01:05:31,690
- 你不是开玩笑 - 我一紧张就想吃
- You're not kidding? - I eat when I'm nervous.

618
01:05:31,700 --> 01:05:35,650
他随时都想吃 他是爱吃鬼
He eats when he's horny. He just likes to eat.

619
01:05:38,800 --> 01:05:41,780
你好吗？
How you doing?

620
01:05:47,570 --> 01:05:50,830
我看他是不会来了
Seems like your boy ain't coming.

621
01:05:51,120 --> 01:05:53,520
