Now what?

622
01:05:54,590 --> 01:05:57,740
他一定会来 相信我
He'll be here. Trust me.

623
01:05:58,270 --> 01:06:02,070
如果我要拿回价值百万的毒品…
Tell me you got a million dollars' worth of my ice?

624
01:06:02,160 --> 01:06:04,470
