- 这是什么？- Y2K
- What's this? - Y2K.

629
01:07:05,710 --> 01:07:07,720
全世界最快的机车
Fastest bike in the world.

630
01:07:07,770 --> 01:07:13,510
碳合金底盘 劳斯莱斯型号直升机喷射引擎
Carbon-fiber chassis buiIt around a Rolls-Royce jet helicopter engine.

