I heard of these.

633
01:07:20,740 --> 01:07:24,770
- 这台车有什么问题？- 它不是我的
- What's wrong with this one? - I don't own it.

634
01:07:24,800 --> 01:07:29,170
- FBI 手举起来 - 手放在头后面
- FBI! Hands where I can see them! - Drop it. Hands behind your head.

635
01:07:29,200 --> 01:07:31,570
- 你想陷害我 - 他们是来抓亨利的
- You tried to set me up. - They're here for Henry.

636
01:07:31,590 --> 01:07:34,720
枪放到地上 把它滑过来
Put the gun on the ground and slide it to me, now.

637
01:07:34,740 --> 01:07:39,120
