so now I can shoot you both.

650
01:08:24,160 --> 01:08:25,990
- 干 - 是啊
- Shit. - Yeah.

651
01:08:26,050 --> 01:08:31,040
- 我该先杀谁呢？- 他 先杀他
- Which one of you guys wants to go first? - Him. Shoot him first.

652
01:08:32,180 --> 01:08:34,790
你确定毒品在里头吗？
You sure the drugs are in there?

653
01:08:43,200 --> 01:08:46,280
