01:10:40,300 --> 01:10:44,330
请求警力支援
Requesting backup at 2000 North Alameda Street.

677
01:10:45,840 --> 01:10:47,920
谢了
Thanks.

678
01:11:46,920 --> 01:11:48,050
不
No, no, no!

679
01:11:48,540 --> 01:11:49,750
等等
Hey, wait!

680
01:12:06,530 --> 01:12:09,890
你这是恶有恶报
Now, ain't that ironic?

681
01:12:20,560 --> 01:12:23,920
- 你没事吧？- 没事 亨利呢？
- You okay? - Yeah. Where's Henry?

682
01:12:24,020 --> 01:12:27,590
- 我要找回那台机车 - 我要去修理那臭婆娘
- I gotta get that bike. - I gotta get that bitch.

683
01:12:27,620 --> 01:12:29,520
没错
Damn right.

684
01:12:44,940 --> 01:12:46,770
- 两位大哥没事吧？- 好痛
- You Power Rangers all right? - That hurt.

685
01:12:46,800 --> 01:12:49,120
- 喂 - 杰
- Hey. - Jay!

686
01:12:49,160 --> 01:12:51,920
我穿了防弹背心
Bulletproof vest, asshole.

687
01:12:51,940 --> 01:12:54,560
可恶 快走
Shit! Let's go!

688
01:12:54,570 --> 01:12:57,090
你一直都是个混球
You were always a punk.

689
01:13:19,700 --> 01:13:22,480
- 你想逃吗？- 你想单挑吗？
- Going somewhere? - You want some of this, bitch?

690
01:13:22,510 --> 01:13:25,330
我就等你这句话
Oh, I thought you'd never ask.

691
01:15:05,480 --> 01:15:08,800
你不该惹老娘的
You messed with the wrong chick!

692
01:15:15,790 --> 01:15:18,820
你才不该惹毛我 臭婆娘
Looks like you did, bitch.

693
01:17:20,620 --> 01:17:23,520
要我载一程吗？
Need a ride?

694
01:17:40,340 --> 01:17:43,840
- 你没事吧？- 死不了
- You all right? - I'll live.

695
01:17:44,580 --> 01:17:47,190
亨利的齿盘 跟凶器吻合
This is Henry's sprocket. It should match the chain...

696
01:17:47,210 --> 01:17:51,280
你朋友说过了 待会再说好吗？
Your friends just told me. Could we maybe do this later?

697
01:17:55,480 --> 01:17:58,800
死了一大堆白人
All these dead white folks around here.

698
01:17:59,040 --> 01:18:02,080
你跟我扯平了
So it look like we done, huh?

699
01:18:04,830 --> 01:18:08,680
- 我为你老弟感到遗憾 - 是啊
- I'm sorry about your brother. - Yeah.

700
01:18:08,710 --> 01:18:13,140
我得走人 我跟警察不对盘
I gotta get out of here. Me and Johnny Law ain't on a first-name basis.

701
01:18:13,170 --> 01:18:15,220
喂
Hey.

702
01:18:15,660 --> 01:18:18,320
- 干嘛？- 谢了
- What? - Thanks.

703
01:18:18,360 --> 01:18:21,620
不用谢 帮我一个忙
Don't sweat it, man. Just do me one favor.

704
01:18:21,660 --> 01:18:26,530
- 什么？- 别闯入我的地盘
- What's that? - Keep your ass out of Inglewood.

705
01:18:39,140 --> 01:18:43,680
我在这世上只有这家店
This shop was the only thing in the world that was really mine.

706
01:18:44,450 --> 01:18:48,180
我可是存了好久的钱才顶下来
Do you have any idea how long it took me to save up for it?

707
01:18:48,220 --> 01:18:50,300
对不起
I'm sorry, Shane.

708
01:18:50,370 --> 01:18:54,890
你脱罪了 也得到你要的了
You're in the clear, so I guess you got what you wanted.

709
01:19:04,330 --> 01:19:08,380
我要的只有你
You're looking at the only reason that I came back.

710
01:19:08,720 --> 01:19:11,940
我只想跟你在一起
I'm betting on more days like that.

711
01:19:13,130 --> 01:19:16,860
你能为我做一件事 福特
You know what you could do for me, Ford?

712
01:19:19,380 --> 01:19:22,600
带我到墨西哥
Take me to Mexico.

713
01:19:30,820 --> 01:19:34,850
- 我们往哪个方向？- 南方
- Where we heading? - South.

714
01:19:35,090 --> 01:19:38,070
我要去接一个人
I got someone to pick up.

715
01:19:41,510 --> 01:19:43,520
狂飚吧
Let's ride.


